#### Getting Started

First load the seed and CSS files, if you haven't yet.

```html
<script src="<%= @getCdnSeed() %>"></script>
<link href="<%= @getBootstrapCSS() %>" rel="stylesheet"></link>
```

Then initialize AlloyUI and load the Scrollspy module.

```javascript
YUI().use(
  'aui-scrollspy',
  function(Y) {
    // code goes here
  }
);
```
---

